OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly but sunny start across
OL,6,Fnorthern and eastern areas. Cloud and
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain across the southwest
OL,8,Fwill slowly move northeastwards
OL,9,Fthrough the day. Sunshine becoming
OL,10,Flimited to northern Scotland and
OL,11,Feastern England by late afternoon.
OL,12,FFeeling warmer.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FLargely cloudy, with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain and drizzle,
OL,16,Fheaviest in the north and west.
OL,17,FTurning windier and for most it will
OL,18,Fbe a warmer night compared to of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
