OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FBands of rain and showers
OL,6,Fmoving eastwards across the country.
OL,7,FThe rain and showers could be heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes. Feeling warm in the sunnier
OL,9,Fbreaks that do develop. Staying breezy.
